\section desc Description
<!-- Short description of what this package is supposed to provide -->

This package contains the TrackAssociator ES Modules, that perform the associaton of reco::Tracks and TrackingParticles in both ways: reco to sim and sim to reco. 
Two kind of associators are implemented: by hits and by chi2.

